description.narrative: Workstream 1 covers our advocacy and communications activities designed to promote the transparency of aid and other financing intended for the relief of poverty and promotion of sustainable development. Publish What You Fund's main targets are the International Aid Transparency Initiative (IATI), the U.S. Government and the European Union, including the governments of France and Germany.
